WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:03.439
The bedrock of all effective leadership is self-awareness.

00:00:04.301 --> 00:00:11.038
Before you can lead a global matrix organization, you must be intimately aware of your own cognitive and emotional architecture.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.073
Your internal values dictate your problem perception, which in turn drives your external actions.
